-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-23/pimco-s-crescenzi-says-bernanke-may-explain-fed-s-low-interest-rate-pledge.html
U.S. Federal Reserve Chairman Ben S.
Bernanke may explain the central bank’s low interest-rate pledge
this week,  Tony Crescenzi , executive vice president and
strategist at Pacific Investment Management Co., said in a
Bloomberg Television interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
